videos.description: Tyler Davis cleans up a miss with a layup and has 8 points early for the Aggies against Kentucky.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Davis starts strong

videos.description: TJ Starks drives along the baseline and draws the foul on his way to putting in a tough layup.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Starks hits layup in traffic

videos.description: Kevin Knox sinks a 3-pointer that gives Kentucky a 37-35 lead going into halftime.
videos.headline: Kentucky takes lead before half

videos.description: Admon Gilder takes the cross-court pass from Tonny Trocha-Morelos and knocks down a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Gilder sinks corner 3

videos.description: Hamidou Diallo throws down a dunk that evens the score at 44-44 for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Diallo ties game with slam

videos.description: DJ Hogg picks up the loose ball and sinks a shot in traffic for the Aggies.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Hogg hits floater in traffic

videos.description: Kevin Knox hits a fast-break layup that gives the Wildcats a 69-67 lead late in the game.
videos.headline: Knox's layup fires up Kentucky crowd

videos.description: John Calipari says he liked what he saw from his team late in their 74-73 win over Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Calipari: 'Like what he saw' in team's maturity

videos.description: Hamidou Diallo leads the No. 21 Wildcats with 18 points in a 74-73 win over the Aggies.
videos.headline: Kentucky edges Texas A&M by a point
